---
description: Formatting standards
alwaysApply: true
---
**Read the rules in this directory before writing or editing any file. Apply every item below — no exceptions, no "close enough."**

These rules apply to **all code you produce, in any context** — including code snippets inside plans, plan files (`.cursor/plans/*.md`), chat responses, and documentation. Planned code must adhere exactly as if it were being committed.

Any rule here can be overridden by a language-specific rule in this directory.

- 4 space indents (no tabs)
- Add linebreak at the end of files, so the last line is empty
